title: Complete Real Friends Discography 2010 - 2014
description:
This is a complete Real Friends Discography. It's contents include all up to date released albums, singles and bonus tracks. I hope it will help you as much as it's helped me and that the days ahead of you are filled with bliss.

Sincerely,

Real Friends' Biggest Fan

PS.

Fuck you Kyle - tap out and go to school near your best friend. You'd probably make a good high school teacher, but this sellout game's going to get old real fast.
